title.narrative: EGYPT-Integrated Irrigation Improvement and Management Project

description.narrative: The overall project objective is to assist the Borrower in improving the management of irrigation and drainage in the Project area to increase the efficiency of irrigated agriculture water use and services (expected to have positive impacts on water distribution quantity, quality, equity and timeliness).
